HEADWORD: Horneophyton
<hw>Horneophyton</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A genus of Devonian fossil
plants considered one of the earliest forms of vascular land plants; it
is similar to genus <gen>Rhynia</gen> but smaller.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Horneophyton</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
